  "description": [
    "Committee Okays Reserve CallUp Power The Senate Armed Services Committee has approved Presi dent Kennedys request for au thority to activate up to 150000 members of the Ready Reserve for a year without declaring a national emergency The vote was unanimous Approval of the bill modified by a minor amendment came after Secretary of Defense Rob ert S McNamara appeared be fore the committee in closed session Amendment The bills amendment provides that authority to extend enlist ments as in last years law would not apply to certain re servists now on active duty In the light of the present in ternational situation Mr McNa mara testified We must be able to respond promptly and deci sively 1961 CallUp Last years Ready Reservist callup permitted the President to call up to 250000 In all 148000 were actually mustered Almost all had returned to their home units by the end of last month Last years law expired on 31 Julv Ready Reservists who were in voluntarily called to active duty last year under Public Law 87117 will be specifically exempted from another mobilization under the new law Fire Chief Lists Safety Hints For Base Personnel National Fire Prevention Week just two"
  ],
